{"id": 1161, "genre": 1001, "title": "酒店设施怎样改进，才真的能吸引到你？", "description": "什么时候你会有“就算冲着这一点也要住这个酒店”的感觉？（题图来自：Louise Rosenkrands）", "record_count": 2976, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160810165650J9a8cdTCLVGtelbp.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-11T03:00:57Z", "options": [{"id": 106756, "content": "极简主义，住酒店要提供和住家里不一样的轻松。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682840}, {"id": 106760, "content": "干净的环境，舒适的床品，合理的布局，有格的装修，还有WI-FI", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705795}, {"id": 106761, "content": "有晾衣架。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644549}, {"id": 106762, "content": "做到能照顾客人的想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026089}, {"id": 106763, "content": "有自己的特色，有娱乐设施，例如说健身房之类的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712180}, {"id": 106765, "content": "卫生间一定一定一定要干净……床褥一定一定一定不能有味道……", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307808}, {"id": 106766, "content": "舒适，干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712190}, {"id": 106767, "content": "厕所不要坐厕。。要蹲厕", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170829}, {"id": 106768, "content": "健身房", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132972}, {"id": 106262, "content": "床垫、枕头都能自行选择软硬", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 106263, "content": "虚拟房卡，用手机就能开房间门", "image": null, "praise_count": 110, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 106264, "content": "把牙刷换成软毛的", "image": null, "praise_count": 169, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 106521, "content": "wifi要稳定和平均", "image": null, "praise_count": 318, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585863}, {"id": 106757, "content": "全新的床上四件套。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698362}, {"id": 106758, "content": "设计感，时尚潮流！W酒店是一种新的风向标", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708327}, {"id": 124678, "content": "隔音、干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781225}, {"id": 106759, "content": "全新的床上四件套，要温暖的颜色。\n落地窗，一整排落地窗。\n外面有微弱的灯光。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698362}, {"id": 127241, "content": "一定要干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807482}, {"id": 109324, "content": "干净清爽，用心一点就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725248}, {"id": 106770, "content": "我觉得酒店在怎么改进还是没有自己的家睡的踏实睡的安心！\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712200}, {"id": 106516, "content": "独特的主题", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707539}, {"id": 106772, "content": "主题搭配独家", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701386}, {"id": 106517, "content": "吸引人的独特的主题", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707539}, {"id": 109333, "content": "温馨独特的设计，干净卫生的环境，面面俱到的服务。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725262}, {"id": 106518, "content": "要美", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 383472}, {"id": 107286, "content": "能够让人放心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713891}, {"id": 106519, "content": "有一点可以抓住女朋友兴趣的，她就会死活拉着我去住！", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690699}, {"id": 106520, "content": "设计感好颜值高。床具洗漱用品品牌好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 340, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668850}, {"id": 108824, "content": "舒适干净，多少要有点特色，环境要搞好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723069}, {"id": 106266, "content": "健身房提供一些当地教练指导的健身课程", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 106522, "content": "干净，做到让人放心的干净。", "image": null, "praise_count": 704, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 106778, "content": "床要舒服卫生设施要干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712231}, {"id": 106523, "content": "好吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423541}, {"id": 106268, "content": "房间之外有更多能让人坐着休息聊天的公共空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 138, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 106524, "content": "厕所弄的再干净卫生一些。", "image": null, "praise_count": 227, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525004}, {"id": 106525, "content": "房间格局设计好，色调好，摆设有特色。", "image": null, "praise_count": 147, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699439}, {"id": 106526, "content": "能在入住后房间内办理Check in", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711359}, {"id": 107550, "content": "随意", "image": "img/option/option/20160814100807f5QgvJcnaD4b23CS", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714624}, {"id": 106528, "content": "健身设施齐全的健身房～", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705899}, {"id": 107552, "content": "走心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714624}, {"id": 106529, "content": "做成高端生态圈酒店，吃喝住玩休闲娱乐在酒店内全解决掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454428}, {"id": 106785, "content": "房间设计布局好，没有烟味", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704838}, {"id": 106531, "content": "床更舒服…治安管理更让人放心………", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708564}, {"id": 106532, "content": "让我想把家装成这样", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479927}, {"id": 106533, "content": "价钱合适。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711398}, {"id": 106534, "content": "灯光足且亮", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689075}, {"id": 106535, "content": "设计独特，色调柔和，摆放简单干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711400}, {"id": 106536, "content": "游泳池和自助餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689075}, {"id": 106537, "content": "你们不考虑钱嘛 性价比要高呀-_-#", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711402}, {"id": 106538, "content": "免费的套套", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697604}]}